7T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da3f35e79d339fdf9a4aa2ee405375209d835593","tid":1814532,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[警世文]<br />\n澄明思諸，勿陷分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係永遠捉唔完，中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面<br />\n<br />\n平心而論，對家要收風根本唔會帶住支槍，帶得支槍入去理大就擺明預咗比你捉，達成佢地分化你地嘅政治目的，既然會有帶住支槍嘅鬼，冇槍喺手嘅鬼都肯定會有㗎啦，黑臉白臉嘅鬼自然都會齊曬，正如連登夠有五毛、TG各公海都一定會有對家臥底，呢個係common sense，有時候根本現場叫捉鬼嘅可能本身都係鬼，而我地亦都唔會咁容易分得清，而比對家輕鬆分化我地，害死手足，所以我再重覆一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面</span>"},{"pid":"42dffb0852f34b0bbfadd30112e7179dc7f405a6","tid":1814532,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"推 呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252756d8d5bf99aa54363b4dcc5862c26f93330e","tid":1814532,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"根本就唔應該討論個啲post<br />\n明顯只係想帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb45f93e2f4a8b8e48cb4a7167c7da9d79f1852","tid":1814532,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n連登仔<br />\n贏就靜靜雞<br />\n港獨又靜靜雞<br />\nQuit game 就大大聲<br />\n捉鬼又大大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fe619cf80d1a7d2afb7d0c76d1172f255f5876f","tid":1814532,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c18bb5349e56827064a54fab68c30baf9b20cbb","tid":1814532,"uid":199739,"like":0,"disl